00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
What is the role of the management of the company?

00:05.000 --> 00:16.000
After we have developed a list of key indicators and reports that we need to understand what is going on in the business,

00:16.000 --> 00:21.000
we usually carry out financial structuring of our company.

00:21.000 --> 00:26.000
In the management accounting there is a concept of financial structure.

00:26.000 --> 00:35.000
It is a combination of the financial responsibilities centers, so-called CFOs, and so-called internal or transfer centers.

00:35.000 --> 00:47.000
In fact, we are trying to determine to what extent the structural divisions of the company are to blame in the size of individual articles, reports on profits and losses of the business as a whole.

00:47.000 --> 00:52.000
The costs, which we see in the reports on profits and losses, arise everywhere.

00:52.000 --> 01:00.000
Accordingly, all structural subdivisions of the company are the centers of costs, because they have a certain budget,

01:00.000 --> 01:06.000
