01:06.000 --> 01:15.000
But it is clear that in addition to the fact that they must fit into the budget, they must ensure the achievement of some goals in terms of quality and time.

01:15.000 --> 01:20.000
But since some structural divisions, in addition to costs, also have income,

01:20.000 --> 01:27.000
these structural divisions are not considered as the centers of costs, but as the centers of so-called gross income or as the centers of profits.

01:27.000 --> 01:35.000
Theoretically, the company can also be a so-called center of income, or centers of income.

01:35.000 --> 01:38.000
This does not mean that these structural divisions have no costs.

01:38.000 --> 01:49.000
It just means that they cannot actively influence any article.

01:49.000 --> 01:59.000
In one trading company, I was shown a financial structure in which the shops selling shoes are listed as the centers of income.

01:59.000 --> 02:07.000
According to the management, there is not a single article of costs that the head of the store and his employees could influence to some extent.

02:07.000 --> 02:13.000
That is, the store is already rented, the place is chosen, it is rented, there is a repair,

02:13.000 --> 02:17.000
