02:42.000 --> 02:46.000
In general, everything is explained in detail in the manual.

02:46.000 --> 02:54.000
If the head of the store and his employees will follow this manual, these rules, this corporate standard, then their income will be large.

02:54.000 --> 02:58.000
If they do not follow it, then the income may be less.

02:58.000 --> 03:06.000
But they did not find a single article of costs that the store employee or the head of the store could influence.

03:06.000 --> 03:10.000
There is an article of theft, the loss of goods from the store.

03:10.000 --> 03:15.000
In this company, this is not an article of costs of the company, this is an article of costs of the staff.

03:15.000 --> 03:21.000
That is, all the loss of goods from the store is from the personal pocket of the employees who work in the store.

03:21.000 --> 03:31.000
But arguing with the management of the company, it can be assumed that the store employees can accidentally or deliberately touch the glass cabinet in the store,

03:31.000 --> 03:38.000
