47:05.000 --> 47:07.000
and to form,

47:07.000 --> 47:09.000
based on the statistics of previous periods,

47:09.000 --> 47:11.000
a reserve for a hopeless

47:11.000 --> 47:13.000
and dubious debitory debt

47:13.000 --> 47:15.000
of each type.

47:15.000 --> 47:17.000
The older the debitory, the more the reserve.

47:17.000 --> 47:19.000
You can subtract these amounts

47:19.000 --> 47:21.000
from the amount of the debitory

47:21.000 --> 47:23.000
